{"tid":1020332,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"單身狗福音！這款虛擬 AI 女友可搭配性愛機器人　陪你度過情人節","createTime":"2019-02-13T13:52:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-13T14:23:13.000Z","uid":212399,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c92661339a563db8ada7eb4ae41bcea34df21392","tid":1020332,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T13:52:50.000Z","msg":"張岑宇／綜合報導<br />\n情人節沒人陪好寂寞？美國性愛機器人公司將於 2 月 14 日推出一款名為 RealDollX 的APP，即使買不起昂貴的性愛機器人，也可以免費下載這款APP擁有一個虛擬的AI女友，她可以和你聊天互動、調情等，陪伴你度過單身的情人節。<br />\n根據《每日郵報》報導，這款APP與同公司推出的性愛機器人 HARMONY 採用的相同人工智慧功能，APP 也可以單獨使用，也可以連結實體的性愛機器人玩偶進行互動。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/tJaFaTFo8lA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FtJaFaTFo8lA&d=uNZXw00WsTXXX%2FAwV3JyER5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=5e1ccc06\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/tJaFaTFo8lA</a><br />\n據《太陽報》報導，使用者還可以建立同時多個不同的女朋友，因為這些虛擬女友們，不會彼此分享他們知道任何關於你的訊息。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.limitlessiq.com/news/post/view/id/8694/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.limitlessiq.com%2Fnews%2Fpost%2Fview%2Fid%2F8694%2F&d=uNZXw00WsTXXX%2FAwV3JyER5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=13e732bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.limitlessiq.com/news/post/view/id/8694/</a>"},{"pid":"18436e01097667199f65559916c00fe88a411c1e","tid":1020332,"uid":231293,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T13:54:29.000Z","msg":"媽呀 好毒呀"},{"pid":"82ee568d59dea55358f5ee30e44ada75a7f2a65f","tid":1020332,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T13:56:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.limitlessiq.com/media/wysiwyg/RAIN/201902/Screenshot-2019-02-11-at-16.51.01.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.limitlessiq.com%2Fmedia%2Fwysiwyg%2FRAIN%2F201902%2FScreenshot-2019-02-11-at-16.51.01.png&h=e39ae84a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.limitlessiq.com/media/wysiwyg/RAIN/201902/Screenshot-2019-02-11-at-16.50.46.png\"